#______________________INPUTS______________________
Inputs (TextField, Select, Autocomplete, Date/Time)
    • Default: size = small, variant = outlined.
    • Height: ≈ 5u (40px).
    • Shape: radius-2 (8px).
    • Outline: 1px, neutral/200 (#B0BEC5).
    • Label: subtitle2 (size 400, weight medium); color text.secondary.
    • [added] Label behavior: use MUI floating label; no custom margins/transforms.
    • [added] Shrink rules: if a placeholder is present → force shrink = true; otherwise shrink = auto (default).
    • Value text: input/value (size 600, weight regular); color text.primary.
    • Helper/Hint: input/helper (size 200, weight regular); color text.secondary.
    • [added] Helper/Counter row: sits below the outline with 4px top gap; put character counters here (never inside the field).
    • Placeholder: text.secondary.
    • Padding: X 2u (16px), Y 1.5u (12px).
    • Focus: outline = primary.main; focus ring = primary overlay 12%; label color = primary.main.
    • Hover: outline neutral/300 (#90A4AE).
    • Disabled: text = text.disabled (#263238 @38%); bg = action.disabled-background (#263238 @12%).
    • [added] Disabled/Focused/Errored states must not move the label position.
    • Invalid/Error: outline + helper text = error.main (#F44336).
    • Success (validated): outline = success.main (#4CAF50).
    • Select/Autocomplete menus: use menu/item-* typography; hover = primary overlay 4%; active = overlay 8% + text primary.main.
    • Chips (multiple select): chip small/medium tokens; hover 4%; selected 8%.
    • Date/Time picker: current-month = token size 700, weight medium; focus ring 12%.
#______________________DATA GRID______________________
Data Grid (MUI X Data Grid)
    • Container: no elevation, 1px outline neutral/200; radius-2 (8px).
    • Header row: bg = surface/paper; text = table/header (size 400, weight medium); divider neutral/200 @ 60%.
    • Row height: 48px.
    • Hover row = primary overlay 4%; selected row = overlay 8% + text primary.main.
    • Focus ring = primary overlay 12%; focus-visible 30%.
    • Cells: body2 (14/regular), color text.primary.
    • Toolbar: search, column chooser, filter, density toggle, export. Icons follow nav rules.
    • Pagination: 10/25/50.
    • Empty = centered body2 text.secondary; error = alert tokens.
#______________________CARDS / WIDGETS______________________
Cards / Widgets
    • Surface: surface/paper.
    • Shape: radius-2 (8px).
    • Border: 1px neutral/200; no shadow.
    • Padding: 3u (24px). Equal height in grids.
    • Header: h6 (size 700, weight medium); optional subtitle subtitle2.
    • Header actions: right-aligned icons; hover 4%, focus 30%, disabled text.disabled.
    • Hover (card): primary overlay 4%.
    • Selected (card): overlay 8%.
    • Dividers: neutral/200 @ 60% only if needed.
    • Empty/loading: skeleton neutral/200; empty = body2 text.secondary.
    • Inline banners: use success/warning/error tokens with correct contrast.
#______________________PRIMARY BUTTON______________________
Primary Button
    • Default: size = small, variant = contained, color = primary.
    • Height: 5u (40px).
    • Padding: X 2u (16px).
    • Shape: radius-2 (8px).
    • Font: button/medium (size 400, weight medium).
    • Background: primary.main (#166CB8).
    • Label color: primary.contrast-text (#FFFFFF).
    • Hover: background = primary.dark (#005AE6).
    • Focus: ring = primary focus overlay 12%; focus-visible 30%.
    • Active: background = primary.dark (#005AE6), overlay 8%.
    • Disabled: background = neutral/200 (#B0BEC5) @ 38%; label = text.disabled.
    • Start/End icon spacing: 8px from label. Icon size 20.
Variants (for consistency)
    • Outlined: border 1px primary.main; text color = primary.main; hover background = primary hover overlay 4%.
    • Text: no border, transparent background; text color = primary.main; hover = overlay 4%.
#______________________ICONS______________________
    • Library: @mui/icons-material (Rounded set).
    • Default size: 24px (nav, inputs, grid, cards).
    • Color tokens: default text.secondary → active primary.main → disabled text.disabled.
    • Fallback: if a specific icon isn’t in @mui/icons-material, use Material Symbols Rounded (font) with the same size/colors.
    